id: pm-xvzm
title: COMMANDS.md omits pm get and pm copy; command-families table missing get/copy/update-many/close-many
description: "docs/COMMANDS.md is the command reference but never documents 'pm get' (the single-item read primitive used throughout AGENT_GUIDE.md:110) or 'pm copy' (core command since PR#146, has MCP tool pm_copy). Both are in PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES. The Command Families table (docs/COMMANDS.md:23-36) also omits update-many/close-many (they have a Bulk Operations section at :117 but no family row). Fix: add get/copy to Triage or a Read family with examples, and add a Bulk family row."
